  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      265.89,
      461.65,
      280.9
    ],
    "text": "Regarding the Disruption of the War Heroes\u2019 Rehearsal Ceremony",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      295.36,
      526.2,
      350.04
    ],
    "text": "A commemorative ceremony is scheduled to be held in front of the War Heroes\u2019 Memorial at the Parliament Grounds under the patronage of His Excellency the President on the occasion of National War Heroes\u2019 Day, which falls on 19.05.2026. In preparation for this main event, a rehearsal of the ceremony was conducted today, 18.05.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      364.6,
      522.05,
      446.9
    ],
    "text": "While the rehearsal and other preparatory arrangements for the main ceremony scheduled for tomorrow were in progress, a group of approximately 35 individuals, including former Member of Parliament Wimal Weerawansa, attempted to enter the War Heroes\u2019 Memorial premises without authorization. This action disrupted the rehearsal activities as well as the official duties of the officers on site. The police intervened promptly, and the group present was removed from the location.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      461.34,
      512.4,
      488.42
    ],
    "text": "In connection with this incident, legal action is scheduled to be initiated against former MP Wimal Weerawansa and the individuals involved.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
